{"tid":1411632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運動只會一直升級，唔會變質","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:23:43.000Z","uid":136431,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7351d8fd16dde14472d6b6c433dcd7bf48019e3e","tid":1411632,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"而家係一層層咁剝開緊港共殖民政權嘅腐敗體制<br />\n爭取普選嘅運動 由2014年到而家都冇停過<br />\n<br />\n當日烏克蘭Euromaidan <br />\n由親歐盟運動，因為政府鎮壓，屢勸不聽一直到最後亞努科維奇收皮，都係升級，唔係變質<br />\n<br />\n總之大家謹記五大訴求，普選行頭，全面追究警黑政權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/anRjbE0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FanRjbE0.gif&h=7f4a4676&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b97a3995ab3c6df32b68edc8cc59137c11b451c","tid":1411632,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">七區集會見</span></span>"},{"pid":"4bb693e5b3c925a33f382dec6006a90a0191ce19","tid":1411632,"uid":293077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9b32b6a435655856ef3639bd7bf0d8823d396d","tid":1411632,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>民間記者會</strong></span></span>"}]}